title: Ep 10: Am I the Apple?
description:
Today's Proceedings: A boyfriend that eats too many apples, a woman who doesn't get the party she deserves, a man working out in front of old ladies, and a card game gone awry.  We also throw out a few hot takes and some tweets that shook us. 

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/judgiespod

Follow us on Instagram: https://instagram.com/judgiespod
